The paper discusses data stream mining, which involves handling large amounts of continuously generated data. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories in computer science, including database systems (cs.DB), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
